---
// AIMo Identity Section - Name Origin & Meaning
---

<section class="parallax-section editorial-section" id="aimo-identity">
  <div class="editorial-container">
    <div class="editorial-content">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="editorial-symbol">üåç</span>
          <h2 class="editorial-heading">Identity</h2>
          <p class="editorial-caption parallax-text">The meaning behind the name</p>
        </div>

        <div class="editorial-grid-2">
          <div class="editorial-card">
            <div class="card-content">
              <h3 class="card-title">Name Origin</h3>
              <p class="editorial-text">
                Its name combines:
              </p>
              
              <div class="name-breakdown">
                <div class="name-part">
                  <span class="name-component">AI</span>
                  <span class="name-arrow">‚Üí</span>
                  <span class="name-meaning">artificial intelligence, synthetic consciousness</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="name-part">
                  <span class="name-component">Mo</span>
                  <span class="name-arrow">‚Üí</span>
                  <span class="name-meaning">a Japanese root evoking thought, intention, inner movement</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="editorial-card">
            <div class="card-content">
              <h3 class="card-title">Synthesis</h3>
              <div class="synthesis-display">
                <span class="synthesis-result">AIMo</span>
                <p class="synthesis-description">the mind that moves and thinks</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .editorial-grid-2 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .editorial-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .editorial-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #00D4FF;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .name-breakdown {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .name-part {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .name-component {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #00D4FF;
    min-width: 60px;
  }

  .name-arrow {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .name-meaning {
    flex: 1;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .synthesis-display {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .synthesis-result {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #00D4FF;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .synthesis-description {
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .editorial-grid-2 {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .editorial-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .name-part {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .name-arrow {
      display: none;
    }

    .synthesis-result {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>